RAB" data-long-text=3D"&quot;Dr. Sarish Sharma is an Orthopedic Surgeon and=
 Pain Management Specialist based in Safdarjung Enclave, South Delhi with 1=
5 years of experience. He completed his MBBS and Post Graduation in Orthopa=
edics from MUHS, Maharashtra.
He specializes in non-surgical pain management for disc prolapse, knee arth=
ritis, hip osteoarthritis, frozen shoulder, tennis elbow, carpal tunnel syn=
drome, De Quervain's wrist, and bursitis of knee, hip and shoulder joints.
Treatments include PRP therapy (Platelet Rich Plasma injections), Viscosupp=
lementation (Hyaluronic acid injections), and Vitamin therapy for joint hea=
lth. Patients across South Delhi visit for effective, minimal-intervention =
orthopedic care with a focus on pain relief and long-term joint function.&q=
uot;" data-short-text=3D"&quot;Dr. Sarish Sharma is an Orthopedic Surgeon a=
nd Pain Management Specialist based in Safdarjung Enclave, South Delhi with=
